column1: Hence  in  all  categories  under  (i)  to  (vi) under  Clause  3:0  there  must  be  63.56
Christian  students.  Since  it  is  63.56  (a  number,  not  a  percentage)  and  there
cannot be a decimal number of students as the decimal number is higher than
0.50, the places available for all Christian students is 64.
